Step 1: initialise environment

```{r}
rm(list=ls())
library(data.table)
library(dplyr)
library(ggplot2)
```

Step 2: Read in Data

```{r}

data <- readRDS("data/output/final_model_data_multiclass__06Oct22.rds")

```

Step 3: Which variables have NAs?

```{r}
for (i in names(data)){
        print(paste0("Number of missings in variable ",i,": ",data[is.na(get(i))] %>% nrow() %>% as.numeric()," out of ",nrow(data)))
}
```
